{
  "stem": "20142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The life in the ghetto was concentrated primarily-- at that time in 1940, the ghetto was established in late October after the-- high-- high Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From some parts of Warsaw, you had to move.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People who were living within this-- this district, they had the-- the-- the-- the comfort of not being-- no, not having the need to move their belongings or anything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were right in the right place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just fortunately that we were living in the ghetto district.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a quite convenient place, because many of these streetworkers crossing like Gasia Street, spelled G-A-S-I-A, today on 11th Street, and Dr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Zamenhof Street that's spelled Z-A-M-E-N-H-O-F Street, the founder of Esperanto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were many other streets, quite famous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nalewki, ?] the center of the bustling [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] industry of-- of-- similar to the Lower East Side in New York.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so these things were providing sufficient amount of dealing with one another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't need outside contact yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There-- there were quite a bit of outside contact through these Jewish people and the Polish people, and they were comin' and going.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But mostly that was-- dealings were done-- were done between one another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my mother and we-- in a rented place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After they established the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were right in the center of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were renting another two rooms to some people who came from the other part of Warsaw where they had to leave their quarters.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then they found some other quarters and they wanted to be independent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not easy to find, but for people who had some kind of financial comfort, they could find whatever they needed.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
